data.title: Dwight Howard led the 2008-2009 Orlando Magic team to the NBA Finals at the age of 23! Beat PHI in the 1st round Beat BOS in the 2nd...
data.meta_description:
1,762 likes, 63 comments - midrangemedia on June 14, 2024: "Dwight Howard led the 2008-2009 Orlando Magic team to the NBA Finals at the age of 23!

Beat PHI in the 1st round 
Beat BOS in the 2nd round
Beat CLE in the Conference Finals 
Lost to the LAL in the Finals

Truly an amazing run and accomplishment at such a young age @dwighthoward 
.
